            "title": "Asana: Don't Believe The AI Studio Hype (Rating Downgrade)",
            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business Colleagues Discussing Strategy At Office\" data-id=\"1314788490\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6490px\" height=\"4327px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1314788490/image_1314788490.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Morsa Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The post-election period has been a tailwind for most stocks, but in particular, many rebound plays that previously fell out of favor with the markets have also seen big gains since November. Asana (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASAN\" title=\"Asana, Inc.\">ASAN</a></span>) is one</p>",
