            "id": "4748472",
            "title": "PHK: Performing Well, But Risks Abound",
            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hand holding American currency\" data-id=\"145671149\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1176px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Anthony Bradshaw</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The PIMCO High Income Fund (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PHK\" title=\"PIMCO High Income Fund\">PHK</a></span>) is a closed-end fund that specializes in providing its investors with a very high level of current income. As is the case with many PIMCO funds, it does fairly well at this, as</p>",
